      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Applicant should be a Permanent Resident of Punjab.\n1. Applicant should be Disabled and the Disability Percentage should be more than 50%.\n1. The Annual Income of Family should not be more than Rs. 60,000/- per Year.\n1. People with mental disabilities are eligible regardless of their specific disability.\n\n",
